00:17:02,043 --> 00:17:03,061
Anatomie.

298
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:05,889
Zweige der Schlüsselbeinschlagader.

299
00:17:05,919 --> 00:17:07,824
Vitamin C und D. V-I-T.

